analysisPopulations.name: Full Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.label: FAS
analysisPopulations.description: All participants who were enrolled, received the study intervention, and completed at least the Baseline questionnaire
analysisPopulations.criteria: Enrolled, received study intervention, completed Baseline questionnaire

analysisPopulations.name: Safety Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.label: SAF
analysisPopulations.description: All participants who received at least one session of the LED face mask and/or neck and chest mask treatment
analysisPopulations.criteria: Received at least one treatment session

analysisPopulations.name: Per-Protocol Population
analysisPopulations.label: PP
analysisPopulations.description: All participants who completed the 12-week study without major protocol deviations and maintained adequate compliance with daily device usage
analysisPopulations.criteria: Completed 12-week study without major protocol deviations

characteristics.name: Age
characteristics.description: Age at baseline in years (25-55 years)

characteristics.name: Sex
characteristics.description: Sex of participant (Female only per inclusion criteria)

characteristics.name: Skin Issues - Fine Lines

characteristics.description: Self-reported presence of wrinkles at baseline

characteristics.name: Skin Issues - Hyperpigmentation
characteristics.description: Self-reported presence of hyperpigmentation at baseline

characteristics.name: Skin Issues - Dark Spots
characteristics.description: Self-reported presence of dark spots at baseline

characteristics.name: Skin Issues - Reduced Elasticity
characteristics.description: Self-reported presence of reduced elasticity at baseline

characteristics.name: Neck and Chest Concerns - Crepey Skin
